      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... it's not just a \"chapter.\" that person is gone. the version of me that had value, that people actually wanted to be around... that person is dead. what's left is just this walking mistake. it doesn't even feel like me anymore. how am i supposed to \"heal\" when there's nothing left to fix? it's like trying to fix a ghost.",
